{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "7141f59d-3c89-4a74-9350-cb9d443b32be",
    "name": "Science2-09-Action and Reaction",
    "sceneId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "b47c4cd0-b1a1-45d5-8f9f-f37fddf85aa8",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "d4a7fb7c-c81d-4f15-9911-4c0fbea755bf",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "648be13e-90a5-4b19-9b5a-fc732406426a",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today we are going to begin an experiment in \"Action and Reaction.\" We will make a device that demonstrates that for every action there is a reaction.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "25dc23a2-77d7-4c93-92c4-1267b915f9d3",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Thus, when you compress magical lightning and project it forward in a beam, you will create a ray that will damage the object it strikes. We will, in fact, create a <i>Zap Gun.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "bdf3a2ce-a646-4da2-90d4-a533ceac6570",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This is a very complicated device. We will be using a miniature steam-powered engine to compress the magical lightning. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "641a55c4-368e-4722-b590-e0b9a75c778f",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We shall start with a demonstration of the steam-powered engine and begin the process of putting the Zap Gun together. Tomorrow we shall finish the construction and test the results.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "41058d91-f428-4434-8abb-4d08adb3f00a",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "ef034867-41d1-49fd-8310-693c27d3ce18",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "293b86bd-dda4-4742-b2e7-595350c4da8e",
                            "text": "Ask About the Doctor's Invention",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "9e65f95d-45ec-4f7f-ac20-77583a164b31",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "72",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "71cf42f4-08d9-4d73-8e8f-d8e9c02bb50d",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dfb001e9-86b8-4f57-a891-bf274b8a1f89",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Is this one of <i>your</i> inventions, Dr. von Braun?",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "36ab0c3b-e8bf-4442-9589-09f7f0d012d8",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, I came up with this idea when I was working on the Science Friction Belt. One of the wires got crossed and the magical rune sprang up and hit me in the head. When I came to, I saw how to reverse the magic effect of the belt to attract incoming force rather than repel it!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e5224e39-83e1-48e3-97af-c20b71c09be5",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Of course, that wouldn't be particularly useful, so I came up with this idea instead.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0f4837f1-1280-4414-a7b8-7ea7e020d049",
                            "text": "Ask About the Zap Gun",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "dd119c42-0f64-4a7e-9e46-e702c6321a6d",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "72",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "72944604-3e82-43a5-b358-ba0cefa8ed71",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5cec3307-09c6-48af-bd65-4ac3c0014ab8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "What exactly does the Zap Gun do?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "aebda653-e464-4e8b-a701-d6857f5d932a",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The Zap Gun sends out a ray of electrical energy that strikes a target and damages it.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1d7e8d44-806f-493f-b13e-f3eb5d3d16aa",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It's a bit tricky to aim a steam-powered engine at a target, so I've attached the engine to a wooden framework. This frame fits comfortably in the hand, allowing you to point the ray towards the bullseye.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a05b871a-0fcf-42f0-a064-f0998c44d59f",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It does a dandy amount of damage, I can assure you.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "079cdc93-b7d7-47e1-a5eb-577222ffd504",
                            "text": "Ask Something Snarky About the Zap Gun",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "802d0f23-5d51-4ffa-a4a6-3c51fbc1a76b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "72",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "bd11a7ba-4b4e-407c-9d13-409ad2dcf738",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "9adafb1e-a0cc-4c77-81d2-1a1643fe10d3",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0a419a64-66a5-4e26-9c41-e525d8c12a2f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Let me see if I get this... We're going to make a miniature steam-powered engine to compress magical energy and we're going to hold it in our hand? Does this mean that one wrong move, the gun explodes, and we'll be disarmed?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "00634b07-ca66-4df2-be7d-ddbba8bb5934",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Nonsense! You won't be disarmed... I'm sure the injuries will heal over time and you'll be as good as new in a couple of months.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e36678c4-ee6a-43c3-b272-a79af24d6387",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c47179c5-4e24-4848-a015-d2e51d64252a",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "All right, people, it's Science Time! ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "3a791e9a-ab76-4f12-ae23-7d73c4886241",
                    "name": "Making a Zap Gun",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "In Science Lab, we made a tiny steam-powered engine to compress magic. Dr. von Braun may be mad, but at least he's never boring."
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}